    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know people say that but it just feels like lying to yourself. like, what's the point of \"small moments\" when the big picture is just total destruction? it's like being on a sinking ship and trying to enjoy a cup of tea. at some point, you have to admit that the struggle is just useless and it's better to just stop fighting it.",
